The response body, route path, simplicity, and test coverage are all correct and meet the spec. The blocking issue is that the implementation uses the wrong TanStack Start API for defining server-side API routes. `createFileRoute` is for React page routes; `createAPIFileRoute` from `@tanstack/react-start` is the correct function for API endpoints. This will cause a runtime failure. The test must also be updated to match the corrected structure.

